### **4. 34_StreamPlotArray**  
**Description:**  
Live-plotting utility for numeric streams, rendered with smooth scrolling and responsive UI.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamPlotArray - Realtime Data Plotter

StreamPlotArray renders incoming values in a dynamic, real-time line chart for metrics, dashboards, and simulation outputs.

## Features
- Live auto-scroll chart  
- Adjustable update speed  
- Lightweight interface  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/34_StreamPlotArray.git
cd 34_StreamPlotArray
python visualize.py
